     H            Y/
     F** AN#RG3 ********************************************
     F*  ANDROID RE-PRINT PICKUP LIST/PALLETIZED LIST      *
     F*                                                    *
     F* TCHK1 07/18/06 CREATE(COPY FROM AB#RG3)            *
     F******************************************************
     FABR6PW1 UF  E           K        DISK
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80K@YMD
     I                                        1   40K@REYY
     I                                        5   60K@REMM
     I                                        7   80K@REDD
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *------------------------------------------------------
      *  MAIN ROUTINE
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@SIRE  4
     C                     PARM           P@DOCK  4
     C                     PARM           P@SHDT  80
     C                     PARM           P@BIN   20
     C                     PARM           P@RLDT  80
     C           K#FW      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@DELY  40
     C                     KFLD           K@DOCK  4
     C                     KFLD           K@SHDT  80
     C                     KFLD           K@SHTM  20
     C                     KFLD           K@REYY
     C                     KFLD           K@REMM
     C                     KFLD           K@REDD
      *
     C                     MOVE P@SIRE    K@DELY
     C                     MOVE P@DOCK    K@DOCK
     C                     Z-ADDP@SHDT    K@SHDT
     C                     Z-ADDP@BIN     K@SHTM
     C                     Z-ADDP@RLDT    K@YMD
      *
     C           K#FW      SETLLABR6PW1
     C           *IN80     DOUEQ*ON
     C           K#FW      READEABR6PW1                  80
     C           *IN80     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WCPRNT
     C                     UPDATABR6PW11
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
